data.description: Welcome to this beautifully updated Chenal Valley home! Located just minutes from shopping and the interstate, this home has 5 bedrooms (or 4 and a bonus room), 3.5 baths, and an office! The whole home has been freshly painted. All light fixtures have been updated(excluding bathroom vanity fixtures), including fans! The kitchen features a gas cooktop, double wall ovens, built-in microwave; newly installed items include quartzite countertops, tile backsplash, composite sink, faucet, and hardware. All bathrooms have newly installed quartzite countertops, sinks, and faucets. The formal dining, office, laundry room, eat in kitchen, living room and primary suite are located on the first floor, while 4 additional rooms and 2 full bathrooms are located upstairs. The primary suite has brand new designer carpet as well as the entire upstairs. This home has an abundance of storage space too! Situated on a flat, fully fenced lot, this home is perfect for entertaining on the covered back patio or in the large backyard!
